        <abstract>
            <p>Continues breeding guinea-pigs to test effects of warmth on gestation period. Concludes period is ten weeks and warmth has no influence. Offers CD the specimens.</p> 
<p>Awaits <hi rend="italic">Variation</hi>.</p> 
